node.text:
Villa Cullinan is the winner of European Property Awards and considered as the Best Residential Property 2019-2020.
​
The mansion has everything for an excepcional, unique and the most luxurious living: value, location, super generous plot, picturesque setting, jaw-dropping views, top-quality construction, cutting-edge equipment, functionality and elegance of interiors, plus that wow factor that makes it truly special.

Casual gathering spaces, floor-to-ceiling windows, panoramic glass doors, state-of-art designer kitchen with premium equipment, amazing covered and sunny outdoor areas, majestic mountain scenery; sea, Africa and Gibraltar views - it is all about this dream house.
By: @drumelia_real_estate
​#TheLuxuryScene

node.text:
Brabus G-Class Limo 😳 What do you think?
​By: @supercarblondie
​#TheLuxuryScene

Have a look at the @jacobandco Astronomia Art Green Dragon 🐉

This timepiece is a prime example of Jacob & Co’s globally recognized watchmaking expertise. It begins with a detailed drawing that, once approved, is rendered to ensure the dragon fits properly within the dial. From this rendering, the 18K rose gold cast is made. This process alone takes more than two months.

Another three months is spent by the artisan to hand-sculpt the details of the dragon. Another craftsman spends approximately 40 hours hand-painting the 18K rose gold cast in green, red and gold acrylic paint. 

Finally, the dragon comes to life with its head upward, fiery ruby eyes and its bright red tongue ablaze.
By: @jacobandco
#TheLuxuryScene #JacobandCo
